                            <comment id="17186866" author="reta" created="Sat, 29 Aug 2020 01:08:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=fernando.las%40gmail.com&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;fernando.las@gmail.com&quot;&gt;fernando.las@gmail.com&lt;/a&gt; ,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It seems like the check &lt;br/&gt;
if (originalProtocol != null || originalRemoteAddr != null) {&lt;br/&gt;
was forgotten during refactorings (part &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-7485&quot; title=&quot;Reverse proxy url is not reflected in Swagger UI response&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CXF-7485&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CXF-7485&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;), the presence of the &quot;use-x-forwarded-headers&quot; and at least some of the X-Forwarded-Xxx headers should be sufficient. Thank you.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Best Regards,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&#160;&#160; Andriy Redko&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
